ed for those external origins.\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- Assistant decided the fix was to update Next.js config rather than change the page logic immediately.\n- It checked the frontend config files, found `frontend/next.config.ts`, and inspected `frontend/package.json`.\n- `package.json` scripts were standard:\n  - `dev`: `next dev`\n  - `build`: `next build`\n  - `start`: `next start`\n- `next.config.ts` initially contained only:\n  - `const nextConfig: NextConfig = { /* config options here */ };`\n- The retained suffix begins where the assistant edits `next.config.ts` to add `allowedDevOrigins` for the blocked external hosts.\n\n<read-files>\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/README.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/package.json\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/domain/entities/settings.entity.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/announcement.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/city.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/course.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/course_student.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/dat_session.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/db.md\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/exam.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/exam_batch.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/lesson.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/license_category.model.ts\n/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be/src/infrastructure/database/models/notification.model.