{"type":"message","id":"aacdfd57","parentId":"1721b6e2","timestamp":"2026-04-23T04:23:19.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mình hiểu — bạn không cần kiểu “print ra được”, mà cần **PDF xuất ra gần như y hệt web**, vẫn giữ:\n- màu nền / card / badge\n- layout bố cục\n- spacing\n- cảm giác dashboard\n\nMình sẽ làm theo hướng **render web thật rồi xuất PDF tự động bằng headless browser**, không dùng print mặc định kiểu đơn giản nữa."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ow4oH3YFnHzGrmxgE2LSjwMK","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which google-chrome || which chromium || which chromium-browser || which chrome || true","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_YXIIWPWPSqLradlw4dztA64G","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"try{require('playwright');console.log('playwright-installed')}catch(e){console.log('playwright-missing')}\"","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_JeEL5cJ8rbvQUR8mpC9JFo85","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport urllib.request\nprint(urllib.request.urlopen('http://127.0.0.1:8787').status)\nPY","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":2273,"output":404,"cacheRead":66944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69621,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776918189043,"responseId":"1776918190482"}}
