{"type":"message","id":"6f6f389d","parentId":"84b593d0","timestamp":"2026-04-23T04:30:38.252Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mình làm luôn phần portal hóa: chuyển report hiện tại thành cấu trúc **report portal** có trang danh sách + trang chi tiết W4, để sẵn cho bước push GitLab và deploy Vercel sau đó."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2m2BzoSAlt3Mnd8XG4cP600p","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/report-portal/index.html","content":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"vi\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>Khương Reports Portal</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./styles.css\" />\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <div class=\"page\">\n      <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Reports Portal</p>\n          <h1>Khương Reports</h1>\n          <p class=\"subtitle\">Cổng lưu trữ và theo dõi báo cáo cá nhân. Mỗi báo cáo có trang riêng, sẵn sàng mở rộng theo tuần/tháng/quý và deploy lên Vercel.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-card\">\n          <div><span>Owner</span><strong>Khương Nịnh</strong></div>\n          <div><span>Portal status</span><strong>Ready for GitLab + Vercel</strong></div>\n          <div><span>Reports</span><strong>1</strong></div>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n\n      <section class=\"section\">\n        <h2>Available Reports</h2>\n        <div class=\"report-grid\">\n          <article class=\"report-card featured\">\n            <p class=\"tag\">Week 4 Review</p>\n            <h3>OKR Progress Report — Start / W2 / W4</h3>\n            <p>Báo cáo đánh giá tiến độ OKR theo ba mốc, tổng hợp từ hệ Multi Agent và các repo AHV DTLX / QLHV.</p>\n            <div class=\"stats\">\n              <div><span>Checkpoint</span><strong>W4</strong></div>\n              <div><span>Objectives</span><strong>4</strong></div>\n              <div><span>Highlight</span><strong>O3, O4</strong></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"./reports/okr-review-w4-2026-04/index.html\">Mở báo cáo</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n  </body>\n</html>"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_QdpBcZiYZP26I6wpzhFSGBX8","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/report-portal/styles.css","content":":root {\n  --bg: #0b1020;\n  --panel: #131a2e;\n  --panel-2: #19233d;\n  --text: #eef3ff;\n  --muted: #9fb0d0;\n  --primary: #6ea8fe;\n  --green: #3ddc97;\n  --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\n  --shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\n}\n*{box-sizing:border-box} body{margin:0;font-family:Inter,ui-sans-serif,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\"Segoe UI\",sans-serif;background:radial-gradient(circle at top,#17213d 0%,var(--bg) 55%);color:var(--text)}\n.page{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 24px 80px}.hero{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:24px;align-items:stretch;margin-bottom:28px}.eyebrow{text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;font-size:12px;color:var(--primary);margin-bottom:8px}h1{margin:0 0 12px;font-size:46px;line-height:1.05}.subtitle{max-width:760px;color:var(--muted);font-size:17px;line-height:1.65}.meta-card,.report-card{background:rgba(19,26,46,.86);border:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:var(--shadow);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-radius:20px}.meta-card{min-width:280px;padding:20px;display:grid;gap:14px}.meta-card span{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-bottom:4px}.meta-card strong{font-size:18px}.section h2{margin:0 0 18px;font-size:28px}.report-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(1,minmax(0,1fr));gap:18px}.report-card{padding:24px}.report-card.featured{border-color:rgba(110,168,254,.4)}.tag{color:var(--primary);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 8px}.report-card h3{margin:0 0 12px;font-size:28px}.report-card p{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}.stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:18px}.stats div{background:var(--panel-2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:14px}.stats span{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-bottom:6px}.stats strong{font-size:20px}.actions{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-top:20px}.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:44px;padding:0 18px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--border);font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer}.btn-primary{color:#07101f;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8ab9ff,#6ea8fe)}@media (max-width:1024px){.hero,.stats{grid-template-columns:1fr;display:grid}h1{font-size:36px}}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":2785,"output":1520,"cacheRead":69376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73681,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776918606442,"responseId":"1776918610024"}}
