{"type":"message","id":"b1b1839b","parentId":"9bdb6ae8","timestamp":"2026-04-23T04:43:43.945Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_kpCAXOMeWmogFPPtOWbq31dL","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"0b66456e9eaad6705df293e18520c36b8a8b1ad3bacb7368b47c18b7199e8bfc\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-21-cms-driving-training-status.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 95,\n      \"endLine\": 166,\n      \"score\": 0.7510925554877749,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7510925554877749,\n      \"snippet\": \"# API Response Format — DTLX Dashboard\\n\\n> **Base URL:** `http://103.253.21.139:5555/api/v1`\\n> **Auth:** Bearer Token (login via `/auth/signin`)\\n> **Branch:** `feature/clean-architecture-migration`\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. `GET /dashboards/reports/profits`\\n\\n**Query Params:** `start_date`, `end_date` (YYYY-MM-DD)\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"success\\\",\\n  \\\"data\\\": {\\n    \\\"revenue\\\": [{ \\\"date\\\": \\\"2026-03-21\\\", \\\"data\\\": 5906262670 }],\\n    \\\"expense\\\": [{ \\\"date\\\": \\\"2026-01-22\\\", \\\"data\\\": 1800000, \\\"label\\\": \\\"Văn Phòng\\\" }],\\n    \\\"profits\\\": [{ \\\"date\\\": \\\"2026-03-21\\\", \\\"data\\\": 5906262670 }],\\n    \\\"arData\\\": [{ \\\"date\\\": \\\"2026-04-05\\\", \\\"data\\\": -4164500000 }],\\n    \\\"studentTrend\\\": [{ \\\"date\\\": \\\"2026-01-17\\\", \\\"data\\\": 1 }],\\n    \\\"teacherTrend\\\": [{ \\\"\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-21-cms-driving-training-status.md#L95-L166\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-21-cms-driving-training-status.md#L95-L166\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"5f9aab3c5fa96ad6ccc6126478ac43120d210f43a9633844de6a77f82e9fd04b\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-22.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 13,\n      \"score\": 0.7212975903967365,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7212975903967365,\n      \"snippet\": \"# 2026-04-22\\n\\n## Session Monitoring Setup\\n- User yêu cầu giám sát master session\\n- Đã setup cron job: `*/5 * * * *` chạy `monitor-session.sh` mỗi 5 phút\\n- Script check session status và alert qua Telegram nếu chết\\n- Log file: `memory/session-monitor.log`\\n\\n## SafeSight AI Project\\n- Hoàn thành specs cho s1-ppe-safety (SafeSight AI)\\n- Frontend demo đang chạy: https://glance-rain-falling-edges.trycloudflare.com\\n- Đã push lên GitLab: pet-connect2/s1-ppe-safety-monitoring (develop branch)\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-22.md#L1-L13\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-22.md#L1-L13\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"557f48b6946a84bda28f0216f8cb591e64a683b1b1109ebb0bc7def85f18a75e\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-19.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 49,\n      \"endLine\": 61,\n      \"score\": 0.7122033191386459,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7122033191386459,\n      \"snippet\": \"- **WORKFLOW RULE (from Khương): Yêu cầu mới → prompt-optimizer → confirm → làm**\\n\\n### Pending\\n- Deploy online: VPS (103.253.21.139) or Cloud (Vercel + Railway)\\n- Backend GitLab repo needs code push\\n- Frontend GitLab repo: `develop` branch has latest code, `main` may be behind\\n\\n### Workspace Paths\\n- `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/` — frontend\\n- `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/maiy-tech-hub-be/` — backend\\n- `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/archive/` — archived old projects\\n- `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/ecosystem/` — OpenSpec specs\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-19.md#L49-L61\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-19.md#L49-L61\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"9db30cb4f7d3464287f9d995d1c89ffe066d629798d1adc0fd1ac2675f2d9655\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-19.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 22,\n      \"endLine\": 57,\n      \"score\": 0.7051117413980298,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7051117413980298,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Admin: `admin@maiy.tech` / `maiy2026`\\n\\n### Server Restart Recovery\\n- After server restart, both frontend and backend had issues\\n- Frontend: dev server not responding → killed old processes, restarted with `yarn dev`\\n- Backend: prisma plugin variable name bug → fixed `src/plugins/prisma.ts`\\n- Both services confirmed 200 OK after fixes\\n\\n### Key Decisions\\n- openclaw.json is active config (not openclaw2.json)\\n- Agent ecosystem is LOCAL ONLY — never push to GitLab\\n- MAIY Tech Hub GitLab = project code only\\n- TikTok simplified to images + caption (manual posting)\\n- Cron jobs: 5 active (draft noon/evening, publish noon/evening, tiktok)\\n\\n### Workflow Rule (from Khương Nịnh, 2026-04-19)\\n- Khi có yê\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-19.md#L22-L57\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-19.md#L22-L57\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ba2b4b9440faa792d843944136025a4868953ceda36a2f9c77ba40541470fe55\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-20.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 66,\n      \"endLine\": 95,\n      \"score\": 0.679523775972178,\n      \"textScore\": 0.679523775972178,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Backend repo: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/ahv-dtlx-backend/`\\n- New branch: `feat/cms-driving-training-design` (created from develop)\\n- Components created: StatsRow.jsx, CalendarSection.jsx, CostTable.jsx, DriverInfo.jsx\\n- Dashboard chart/index.jsx updated\\n- Frontend: Vite + React + Ant Design + Redux\\n- Backend: Express + TypeORM + MongoDB\\n\\n### Infrastructure Setup\\n- Frontend dev server: port 3002 → http://103.253.21.139:3002\\n- Backend: port 5555 → http://103.253.21.139:5555\\n- MongoDB: port 27017 (Docker, image mongo:7)\\n- Vite proxy configured: `/api` → `http://localhost:5555`\\n- Frontend .env: VITE_PORT=3002, VITE_API_SERVER= (empty → relative URLs via proxy)\\n- B\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-20.md#L66-L95\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-20.md#L66-L95\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"mode\": \"fts-only\"\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"id":"0b66456e9eaad6705df293e18520c36b8a8b1ad3bacb7368b47c18b7199e8bfc","path":"memory/2026-04-21-cms-driving-training-status.md","startLine":95,"endLine":166,"score":0.7510925554877749,"textScore":0.7510925554877749,"snippet":"# API Response Format — DTLX Dashboard\n\n> **Base URL:** `http://103.253.21.139:5555/api/v1`\n> **Auth:** Bearer Token (login via `/auth/signin`)\n> **Branch:** `feature/clean-architecture-migration`\n\n---\n\n## 1. `GET /dashboards/reports/profits`\n\n**Query Params:** `start_date`, `end_date` (YYYY-MM-DD)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"revenue\": [{ \"date\": \"2026-03-21\", \"data\": 5906262670 }],\n    \"expense\": [{ \"date\": \"2026-01-22\", \"data\": 1800000, \"label\": \"Văn Phòng\" }],\n    \"profits\": [{ \"date\": \"2026-03-21\", \"data\": 5906262670 }],\n    \"arData\": [{ \"date\": \"2026-04-05\", \"data\": -4164500000 }],\n    \"studentTrend\": [{ \"date\": \"2026-01-17\", \"data\": 1 }],\n    \"teacherTrend\": [{ \"\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-21-cms-driving-training-status.md#L95-L166","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-21-cms-driving-training-status.md#L95-L166","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"5f9aab3c5fa96ad6ccc6126478ac43120d210f43a9633844de6a77f82e9fd04b","path":"memory/2026-04-22.md","startLine":1,"endLine":13,"score":0.7212975903967365,"textScore":0.7212975903967365,"snippet":"# 2026-04-22\n\n## Session Monitoring Setup\n- User yêu cầu giám sát master session\n- Đã setup cron job: `*/5 * * * *` chạy `monitor-session.sh` mỗi 5 phút\n- Script check session status và alert qua Telegram nếu chết\n- Log file: `memory/session-monitor.log`\n\n## SafeSight AI Project\n- Hoàn thành specs cho s1-ppe-safety (SafeSight AI)\n- Frontend demo đang chạy: https://glance-rain-falling-edges.trycloudflare.com\n- Đã push lên GitLab: pet-connect2/s1-ppe-safety-monitoring (develop branch)\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-22.md#L1-L13","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-22.md#L1-L13","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"557f48b6946a84bda28f0216f8cb591e64a683b1b1109ebb0bc7def85f18a75e","path":"memory/2026-04-19.md","startLine":49,"endLine":61,"score":0.7122033191386459,"textScore":0.7122033191386459,"snippet":"- **WORKFLOW RULE (from Khương): Yêu cầu mới → prompt-optimizer → confirm → làm**\n\n### Pending\n- Deploy online: VPS (103.253.21.139) or Cloud (Vercel + Railway)\n- Backend GitLab repo needs code push\n- Frontend GitLab repo: `develop` branch has latest code, `main` may be behind\n\n### Workspace Paths\n- `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/` — frontend\n- `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/maiy-tech-hub-be/` — backend\n- `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/archive/` — archived old projects\n- `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/ecosystem/` — OpenSpec specs\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-19.md#L49-L61","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-19.md#L49-L61","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"9db30cb4f7d3464287f9d995d1c89ffe066d629798d1adc0fd1ac2675f2d9655","path":"memory/2026-04-19.md","startLine":22,"endLine":57,"score":0.7051117413980298,"textScore":0.7051117413980298,"snippet":"- Admin: `admin@maiy.tech` / `maiy2026`\n\n### Server Restart Recovery\n- After server restart, both frontend and backend had issues\n- Frontend: dev server not responding → killed old processes, restarted with `yarn dev`\n- Backend: prisma plugin variable name bug → fixed `src/plugins/prisma.ts`\n- Both services confirmed 200 OK after fixes\n\n### Key Decisions\n- openclaw.json is active config (not openclaw2.json)\n- Agent ecosystem is LOCAL ONLY — never push to GitLab\n- MAIY Tech Hub GitLab = project code only\n- TikTok simplified to images + caption (manual posting)\n- Cron jobs: 5 active (draft noon/evening, publish noon/evening, tiktok)\n\n### Workflow Rule (from Khương Nịnh, 2026-04-19)\n- 