{"type":"message","id":"9143137e","parentId":"e6fa122a","timestamp":"2026-04-23T06:14:46.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create a nice overview page for the multi-agent governance docs in the portal. I'll create a comprehensive HTML page that shows all 9 documents with descriptions and links to each markdown file.","thinkingSignature":"bc6112d3fd4a78de85d51fa614a7ae62bfd8bbf11c962716bc4530df5f4ac9a7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l3r5mnuvv372_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/report-portal/reports/multi-agent-governance/index.html","content":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"vi\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>Multi-Agent Ecosystem Documentation — Khương Reports</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"../../styles.css\" />\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <div class=\"page\">\n      <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Agent Governance Suite</p>\n          <h1>Multi-Agent Ecosystem Documentation</h1>\n          <p class=\"subtitle\">Bộ tài liệu đầy đủ về hệ Multi-Agent: từ tổng quan, taxonomy, orchestration, workflows, spec framework, governance, metrics, gap analysis, đến case studies thực chiến. Tổng cộng <strong>9 tài liệu, 2,072 dòng</strong>.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-card\">\n          <div><span>Prepared by</span><strong>Khương Nịnh</strong></div>\n          <div><span>Documents</span><strong>9</strong></div>\n          <div><span>Total content</span><strong>2,072 lines</strong></div>\n          <div><span>Status</span><strong>Ready for Confluence</strong></div>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n\n      <section class=\"summary-grid\">\n        <article class=\"summary-card strong\">\n          <span>Maturity Stage</span>\n          <h3>Level 2–3</h3>\n          <p>Repeatable → Defined</p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"summary-card\">\n          <span>Gaps Identified</span>\n          <h3>9 Gaps</h3>\n          <p>Prioritized by severity and impact</p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"summary-card\">\n          <span>Canonical Workflows</span>\n          <h3>5 Workflows</h3>\n          <p>Docs, Code Review, Architecture, Feature Spec, QA</p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"summary-card\">\n          <span>Agent Taxonomy</span>\n          <h3>4 Layers</h3>\n          <p>Control / Reusable / Domain / Temporary</p>\n        </article>\n      </section>\n\n      <section>\n        <h2>Document Suite Overview</h2>\n        <div class=\"objective-grid\">\n          <article class=\"objective-card featured\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Doc 01</p>\n                <h3>Multi-Agent Ecosystem Overview</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status strong\">Foundation</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>Tổng quan toàn cảnh hệ Multi-Agent: mục đích, cấu trúc, operating intent, maturity assessment, và strategic recommendations.</p>\n            <ul class=\"doc-highlights\">\n              <li>Ba đặc điểm chính của hệ hiện tại</li>\n              <li>Đánh giá maturity: Strengths vs Weaknesses</li>\n              <li>Strategic recommendation cho bước tiếp theo</li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"../../../../docs/01-multi-agent-overview.md\" download>Download MD</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card featured\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Doc 02</p>\n                <h3>Agent Taxonomy and Inventory</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status strong\">Foundation</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>Mô hình phân loại 4 lớp agent và danh sách inventory đầy đủ: Control, Reusable Capability, Domain-Specific, Temporary.</p>\n            <ul class=\"doc-highlights\">\n              <li>Phân loại 65+ agents theo layer</li>\n              <li>Capability clusters: Engineering, QA, Product, Content, Design, Operations</li>\n              <li>Recommended registry fields</li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"../../../../docs/02-agent-taxonomy-and-inventory.md\" download>Download MD</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Doc 03</p>\n                <h3>Orchestration Architecture</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status ontrack\">Operating</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>Mô hình kiến trúc điều phối: intake, routing, specialist execution, consolidation, delivery. Bao gồm routing decision tree và escalation model.</p>\n            <ul class=\"doc-highlights\">\n              <li>6-stage intake model</li>\n              <li>Routing decision tree</li>\n              <li>Standard handoff contract format</li>\n              <li>Escalation triggers và path</li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"../../../../docs/03-orchestration-architecture.md\" download>Download MD</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Doc 04</p>\n                <h3>Standard Workflows</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status ontrack\">Operating</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>5 canonical workflows chuẩn: Documentation Creation, Code Review, Architecture Design, Feature Specification, QA and Test Planning.</p>\n            <ul class=\"doc-highlights\">\n              <li>5 workflows với stage-by-stage breakdown</li>\n              <li>Agents involved per workflow</li>\n              <li>Escalation triggers tại mỗi stage</li>\n              <li>Expected outputs và quality gates</li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"../../../../docs/04-standard-workflows.md\" download>Download MD</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Doc 05</p>\n                <h3>Agent Specification Framework</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status ontrack\">Operating</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>Khuôn mẫu chuẩn để document mọi agent: 11 sections bắt buộc, ví dụ spec hoàn chỉnh, và migration strategy.</p>\n            <ul class=\"doc-highlights\">\n              <li>11 required sections cho AGENTS.md</li>\n              <li>Well-structured example spec</li>\n              <li>Authorization levels model</li>\n              <li>Migration strategy cho existing agents</li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"../../../../docs/05-agent-spec-framework.md\" download>Download MD</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Doc 06</p>\n                <h3>Governance and Operating Model</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status ontrack\">Operating</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>Chính sách vận hành: authorization levels, file modification rules, external communication policy, escalation, workflow governance, agent lifecycle, safety.</p>\n            <ul class=\"doc-highlights\">\n              <li>4 authorization levels (Level 1–4)</li>\n              <li>Prohibited actions (absolute)</li>\n              <li>Agent creation và retirement process</li>\n              <li>Audit and traceability model</li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"../../../../docs/06-governance-and-operating-model.md\" download>Download MD</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Doc 07</p>\n                <h3>Metrics, KPIs and Adoption Model</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status ontrack\">Operating</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>Bộ metrics toàn diện: 4 categories — Adoption, Quality, Efficiency, Outcome. Bao gồm dashboard structure, reporting cadence, và maturity model.</p>\n            <ul class=\"doc-highlights\">\n              <li>13 specific metrics across 4 categories</li>\n              <li>Executive / Operational / Agent-level dashboards</li>\n              <li>Adoption maturity model (5 levels)</li>\n              <li>Current assessment: Level 2–3</li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"../../../../docs/07-metrics-kpis-and-adoption.md\" download>Download MD</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Doc 08</p>\n                <h3>Gap Analysis and Roadmap</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status ontrack\">Operating</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>Phân tích 9 gaps còn thiếu: từ inconsistent documentation đến no retirement policy. Priority matrix + phased roadmap 3 giai đoạn.</p>\n            <ul class=\"doc-highlights\">\n              <li>9 gaps evaluated by severity, urgency, effort, impact</li>\n              <li>Priority matrix với action ordering</li>\n              <li>3-phase roadmap: Foundational → Operating Standards → Maturity</li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"../../../../docs/08-gap-analysis-and-roadmap.md\" download>Download MD</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Doc 09</p>\n                <h3>Case Studies</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status ontrack\">Operating</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>5 case studies thực chiến: Documentation System Build, Code Review, Feature Specification, System Performance Review, OKR Assessment.</p>\n            <ul class=\"doc-highlights\">\n              <li>5 case studies với full context, workflow, outcomes</li>\n              <li>Lessons learned thực tế</li>\n              <li>Case study template cho future use</li>\n            </ul>\n            <div class=\"actions\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"../../../../docs/09-case-studies.md\" download>Download MD</a>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"footer-note\">\n        <h2>Management Conclusion</h2>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Hệ Multi-Agent hiện tại ở <strong>maturity Level 2–3</strong>: workflows có tồn tại nhưng chưa đồng đều và chưa được đo lường có hệ thống.</li>\n          <li>9 gaps đã được xác định và ưu tiên theo severity và impact. Top 5 gaps cần giải quyết trước trong 1–3 tháng.</li>\n          <li>Hệ thống đã chứng minh giá trị qua 5 case studies thực chiến. Bước tiếp theo là <strong>chuẩn hóa, đo lường, và mở rộng</strong>.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:20px; color:var(--muted);\">Bộ tài liệu này sẵn sàng để review và publish lên Confluence.</p>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n  </body>\n</html>\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":76,"output":2898,"cacheRead":133017,"cacheWrite":1712,"totalTokens":137703,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776924846999,"responseId":"0638ebb0c260ac3b3592bb9e8023ae10"}}
