{"type":"message","id":"7095fef6","parentId":"3569bf21","timestamp":"2026-04-23T06:54:48.630Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All pages are accessible. Let me give the user the final summary with all the URLs.","thinkingSignature":"e5a1ec155d202463a394929d332cdf403464967badcd0dbc96bada4dbb14175e"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] **Xong hoàn toàn rồi.** Giờ bạn có thể **đọc trên web** và **tải về** cho tất cả 9 tài liệu.\n\n### Các link truy cập\n\n#### Trang chủ portal\n<http://103.253.21.139:8790>\n\n#### Bộ Multi-Agent Documentation — Hub\n<http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/multi-agent-governance/index.html>\n\n---\n\n### Đọc từng tài liệu trên web\n\n| # | Tài liệu | Link |\n|---|---|---|\n| 01 | Multi-Agent Ecosystem Overview | [📖 Đọc](http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/multi-agent-governance/01-multi-agent-overview.html) |\n| 02 | Agent Taxonomy and Inventory | [📖 Đọc](http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/multi-agent-governance/02-agent-taxonomy-and-inventory.html) |\n| 03 | Orchestration Architecture | [📖 Đọc](http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/multi-agent-governance/03-orchestration-architecture.html) |\n| 04 | Standard Workflows | [📖 Đọc](http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/multi-agent-governance/04-standard-workflows.html) |\n| 05 | Agent Spec Framework | [📖 Đọc](http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/multi-agent-governance/05-agent-spec-framework.html) |\n| 06 | Governance and Operating Model | [📖 Đọc](http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/multi-agent-governance/06-governance-and-operating-model.html) |\n| 07 | Metrics, KPIs and Adoption | [📖 Đọc](http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/multi-agent-governance/07-metrics-kpis-and-adoption.html) |\n| 08 | Gap Analysis and Roadmap | [📖 Đọc](http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/multi-agent-governance/08-gap-analysis-and-roadmap.html) |\n| 09 | Case Studies | [📖 Đọc](http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/multi-agent-governance/09-case-studies.html) |\n\n---\n\n### Tải file Markdown gốc\nMỗi trang đọc trên web đều có nút **\"Tải .md\"** để download file gốc.\n\n---\n\n### Tóm tắt những gì đã có\n- **9 tài liệu HTML** — đọc trên web, responsive, có màu\n- **9 file Markdown** — tải về máy\n- **trang hub** — danh sách tất cả tài liệu, có nút đọc/tải cho từng cái\n- **OKR Report W4** — <http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/okr-review-w4-2026-04/index.html>\n\n---\n\nBước tiếp theo là **publish lên Confluence** — khi nào bạn review xong và ok rồi, nhắn mình làm tiếp."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":135,"output":792,"cacheRead":151799,"cacheWrite":466,"totalTokens":153192,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776927273804,"responseId":"0638f52b72452631d7ca105897e0987e"}}
