{"type":"message","id":"0648abb9","parentId":"dedf8ff0","timestamp":"2026-04-23T06:59:05.041Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"5806\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khuong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-23 06:59 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khuong (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khuong\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nCấu trúc ổn tùy hiên hệ thống agent chỉ có hơn 40 một số agent có prefix dạng ahv-dtlx, etc đó là những agent được khởi tạo session riêng cho dự án đó nên sửa lại"}],"timestamp":1776927545023}}
{"type":"message","id":"efe7aca9","parentId":"0648abb9","timestamp":"2026-04-23T06:59:29.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying the agent count is actually around 40, not 65. The ahv-dtlx prefix agents are project-specific agents that have their own dedicated sessions. These are project-scoped agents, not all part of the same reusable ecosystem.\n\nSo the taxonomy should be updated to reflect:\n- Total agents: ~40\n- Some have ahv-dtlx prefix - these are project-specific sessions for the DTLX project\n- The taxonomy needs to be corrected\n\nLet me recount the agents more carefully. Looking at the earlier output, the agents were:\n1. agile-product-owner\n2. ahv-dtlx-agile\n\n\n3. ahv-dtlx-architect\n4. ahv-dtlx-be\n5. ahv-dtlx-clean\n6. ahv-dtlx-content-engine\n7. ahv-dtlx-content-strategy\n8. ahv-dtlx-db-schema\n9. ahv-dtlx-devops\n10. ahv-dtlx-docs\n11. ahv-dtlx-epic\n12. ahv-dtlx-fe\n13. ahv-dtlx-harness\n14. ahv-dtlx-market\n15. ahv-dtlx-perf\n16. ahv-dtlx-playwright\n17. ahv-dtlx-product-strategy\n18. ahv-dtlx-prompt\n19. ahv-dtlx-qa\n20. ahv-dtlx-review\n21. ahv-dtlx-security\n22. ahv-dtlx-senior-security\n23. ahv-dtlx-seo\n24. ahv-dtlx-shadcn\n25. ahv-dtlx-standards\n26. ahv-dtlx-stitch\n27. ahv-dtlx-ui-design\n28. ahv-dtlx-ui-ux\n29. ai-seo\n30. article-writing\n31. clean-code\n32. code-reviewer\n33. coding-standards\n34. content-engine\n35. content-strategy\n36. database-reviewer\n37. database-schema-designer\n38. deep-research\n39. documentation-lookup\n40. epic-design\n41. harness-optimizer\n42. market-intelligence\n43. master-orchestrator\n44. performance-optimizer\n45. planner\n46. playwright-pro\n47. product-marketing-context\n48. product-strategy\n49. prompt-optimizer\n50. realistic-seeder\n51. refactor-cleaner\n52. security-reviewer\n53. senior-architect\n54. senior-backend\n55. senior-devops\n56. senior-frontend\n57. senior-qa\n58. senior-security\n59. seo-audit\n60. shadcn-expert\n61. stitch-design\n62. stitch-loop\n63. typescript-reviewer\n64. ui-design-system\n65. ui-ux-pro-max\n\nSo there are actually 65 agents total, not 40 as the user stated. The ahv-dtlx prefixed ones are project-specific sessions created for the DTLX project. I should clarify this discrepancy with the user and offer to update the documentation to accurately reflect the actual count.","thinkingSignature":"f622ac359b5958faef5d1d0388eb9d791d5f8c132639f5a4d347cee8e4ac75dd"},{"type":"text","text":"Mình hiểu rồi. Mình đã đếm thấy **65 agent** trong hệ, nhưng ý bạn là:\n- một số agent có prefix `ahv-dtlx` — đó là **session riêng cho dự án DTLX**, không phải agent hệ thống\n- tổng agent hệ thống thực tế **ít hơn ~40**\n\nMình sẽ đếm lại chính xác và cập nhật tài liệu.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vduz7xtdrwgp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review -maxdepth 2 -name AGENTS.md | sed 's#/AGENTS.md##' | sort | grep -v '/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-' | sed 's#.*/##' | wc -l","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vduz7xtdrwgp_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review -maxdepth 2 -name AGENTS.md | sed 's#/AGENTS.md##' | sort | grep -v '/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/ahv-dtlx-' | sed 's#.*/##' | sort","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vduz7xtdrwgp_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review -maxdepth 2 -name AGENTS.md | sed 's#/AGENTS.md##' | sort | grep '/ahv-dtlx-' | sed 's#.*/##' | wc -l","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":1133,"cacheRead":151482,"cacheWrite":1137,"totalTokens":153752,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776927545042,"responseId":"0