{"type":"message","id":"1d8c9971","parentId":"ef91b67f","timestamp":"2026-04-23T07:24:20.370Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_y40bl7zsbyua_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-23.md'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-23.md'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776929060369}}
{"type":"message","id":"25e39f69","parentId":"1d8c9971","timestamp":"2026-04-23T07:24:51.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file doesn't exist, so I need to create it. Let me write all the durable memories from this session.","thinkingSignature":"8e47e8928e32573fe7c74b8282ac60caa083e1e41d3a861072a6d10e02b9b677"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mgdauee14syd_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-23.md","content":"# Memory — 2026-04-23\n\n## Today's Session Summary\n\n### User Context\n- **User:** Khương Nịnh / Khuong (Telegram: @khuowgn, ID: 6053576134)\n- **Role:** Developer/tech lead managing multiple projects at AHV Tech Hub\n- **Working on:** AHV QLHV, Landing Page V2, AHV DTLX CMS, Multi AI Agent initiative\n- **Language preference:** Vietnamese\n\n### Projects Discussed Today\n\n#### AHV Landing Page V2\n- Group: AHV Landing Page\n- Status: Production, currently in **maintenance + enhancement mode**\n- Responsibilities: handle change requests, maintain stability, small UX improvements\n\n#### AHV DTLX CMS Trung tâm\n- Group: AHV DTLX\n- Scope: **Refactor + Optimize + Architecture migration + Frontend redesign**\n- Status: Ongoing\n\n#### AHV DTLX → QLHV (CMS thầy giáo)\n- Group: AHV DTLX\n- Scope: **Build from scratch, FE + BE**\n- Status: Active development with strong commit history\n- FE repo: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-fe` (branch `fix/sat-hach-map-error`, updated to `origin/develop` at commit `815c670`)\n- BE repo: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/projects/ahv-qlhv-be` (branch `develop`, updated to commit `4ff139c`)\n- Recent FE commits: dashboard, exam UI, student import, finance reporting, support request, role-based nav, CI/CD\n- Recent BE commits: RBAC, teacher data isolation, support request module, finance/import flows, swagger 18 modules/100+ endpoints, CI/CD/Docker\n\n### OKR Work — Khương Nịnh's Personal OKRs\n\n**4 Objectives established:**\n\n**O1: AHV Landing Page V2** (maintenance/production)\n- 5 KRs: stable production, handle CRs, release quality control, UX improvements, changelog maintenance\n\n**O2: CMS Trung tâm Refactor** (refactor/optimize/architecture/redesign)\n- 5 KRs: refactor modules, optimize bottlenecks, migrate architecture, redesign frontend, quality control\n\n**O3: QLHV Build FE+BE from scratch**\n- 5 KRs: FE foundation, BE foundation, FE-BE integration, code/arch/docs standards, internal review readiness\n- Evidence: very strong, 103/122 FE commits (W2/W4), 93/155 BE commits (W2/W4), swagger 18 modules\n\n**O4: Multi AI Agent**\n- 5 KRs: research models, build workflow/architecture, apply to real use cases, document guidelines, create reusable platform\n- Evidence: 65 agents total (38 system/generic + 27 DTLX-specific with `ahv-dtlx-` prefix)\n\n### Multi-Agent Ecosystem Documentation Suite\n\nBuilt a complete documentation set for the multi-agent ecosystem:\n\n**Total: 11 documents created:**\n- `docs/01-multi-agent-overview.md` — ecosystem overview, maturity assessment\n- `docs/02-agent-taxonomy-and-inventory.md` — 4-layer taxonomy, 65 agents (38 system + 27 DTLX)\n- `docs/03-orchestration-architecture.md` — intake model, routing tree, handoff contracts, escalation\n- `docs/04-standard-workflows.md` — 5 canonical workflows: Docs, Code Review, Architecture, Feature Spec, QA\n- `docs/05-agent-spec-framework.md` — 11-section agent spec template\n- `docs/06-governance-and-operating-model.md` — 4 auth levels, lifecycle, safety rules\n- `docs/07-metrics-kpis-and-adoption.md` — 13 metrics across 4 categories, maturity model (Level 2-3)\n- `docs/08-gap-analysis-and-roadmap.md` — 9 gaps, priority matrix, 3-phase roadmap\n- `docs/09-case-studies.md` — 5 real case studies + template\n- `docs/10-non-tech-guide.md` — user guide for non-technical people (10 sections)\n- `docs/10b-system-architecture-diagram.md` — full system architecture diagrams\n\n**Hub portal:** `docs/report-portal/reports/multi-agent-governance/index.html`\n**Running at:** http://103.253.21.139:8790\n\n### Agent Taxonomy Confirmed\n- **38 system/generic agents** — reusable across projects (senior-frontend, code-reviewer, prompt-optimizer, etc.)\n- **27 DTLX project-specific agents** — prefixed `ahv-dtlx-`, created as dedicated sessions for AHV DTLX project\n- **4 layers:** Control / Reusable Capability / Domain-Specific / Temporary\n- **5 canonical workflows** defined\n\n### Report Portal\n- Location: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/report-portal/`\n- Running at: http://103.253.21.139:8790\n- Contains: OKR W4 report + Multi-Agent governance suite hub\n\n### SafeSight AI (safety app)\n- Frontend: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/safesight-ai/frontend`\n- Running local: http://localhost:3001\n- Public tunnel: https://introductory-government-imagination-sept.trycloudflare.com\n- Issue: dev mode blocking cross-origins — fixed via `allowedDevOrigins` in next.config.ts\n\n### Confluence Pages Created\n- AHV QLHV space: multiple pages created (Overview, Business Analysis, DB Documentation, Architecture, Technical, API)\n- Pages marked as \"Clean\" versions due to markdown rendering issues\n\n### Decisions Made\n- OKR structure: 4 objectives (not merged O2 into one)\n- O2 (CMS Trung tâm) = separate from O3 (QLHV build)\n- Landing Page V2 = maintenance mode, not new build\n- Agent ecosystem split: 38 system + 27 DTLX-specific\n- Report portal chosen over per-report repos for GitHub structure\n- Next step: publish Multi-Agent docs to Confluence\n\n### Pending Items\n- VPS bot activation at 161.248.81.141 (SSH details not yet confirmed)\n- Chromium install for PDF export (needed sudo/elevated access)\n- GitLab group creation for report portal (need repo details from user)\n- Vercel deployment for report portal\n- Publish Multi-Agent docs to Confluence\n\n## Key Learnings\n- User prefers detailed, professional, academic-level Vietnamese writing\n- User wants step-by-step progress updates every 2-3 minutes during long tasks\n- User wants all output to be \"web-ready\" and downloadable\n- User needs both technical and non-technical documentation\n- Agent system has clear 2-population structure: generic vs DTLX-specific\n- Confluence markdown rendering is problematic — prefer HTML/conversion approach\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":81,"output":1579,"cacheRead":125217,"cacheWrite":937,"totalTokens":127814,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776929060376,"responseId":"0638fc26fba78be064d772b6482ac547"}}
