{"type":"message","id":"c95b9a35","parentId":"bab3f4cb","timestamp":"2026-04-23T07:56:05.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full file. Let me create the merged version:\n\n- O2: Merge CMS Trung tâm Refactor + AHV DTLX → QLHV Build\n- Rename O3 to O2 (merged), rename O4 to O3\n\nNew merged O2 (AHV DTLX — Build & Evolve):\n- KR2.1: Nền tảng FE + BE mới (QLHV from scratch)\n- KR2.2: Integration FE-BE và end-to-end flows\n- KR2.3: Refactor & optimize CMS Trung tâm\n\n\n- KR2.4: Chuẩn hóa code, kiến trúc, docs\n- KR2.5: Review/demo readiness\n\nI need to recalculate the overall scores for the new O2 by averaging across all five key results for each time period, which gives me a baseline of 0.17 at the start, jumping to 0.47 by W2.\n\nFor the detailed KRs, I'm now breaking down each one with specific metrics: the QLHV foundation work scores highest at 0.80, the integration and end-to-end flows are solid at 0.78, the CMS refactoring sits at a moderate 0.63, standardization and docs are on track at 0.70, and review readiness is tracking well at 0.72.\n\nNow I need to shift everything down—renaming the old O4 to O3—and regenerate the full HTML file with these updated labels and consolidated sections.","thinkingSignature":"cd89c7f88ada4c2bf51682dd14ebf2308a60aaae5cf08b7cba5be54e28dfde6c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zf298jkpp2k5_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/okr-report/index.html","content":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"vi\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>OKR Report Dashboard - Khương Nịnh</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./styles.css\" />\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <div class=\"page\">\n      <header class=\"hero\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Performance Review Dashboard</p>\n          <h1>OKR Progress Report</h1>\n          <p class=\"subtitle\">\n            Báo cáo đánh giá OKR cá nhân theo 3 mốc <strong>Start → W2 → W4</strong>,\n            tổng hợp từ hệ agent hiện tại và các repo dự án AHV.\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"toolbar no-print\">\n            <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" onclick=\"window.print()\">Xuất PDF</button>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"./index.html\" download=\"okr-report-dashboard.html\">Tải file HTML</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"meta-card\">\n          <div><span>Owner</span><strong>Khương Nịnh</strong></div>\n          <div><span>Checkpoint</span><strong>Week 4</strong></div>\n          <div><span>Reviewed at</span><strong>2026-04-23</strong></div>\n          <div class=\"print-hint no-print\"><span>Export</span><strong>Ctrl/Cmd + P → Save as PDF</strong></div>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n\n      <section class=\"summary-grid\">\n        <article class=\"summary-card strong\">\n          <span>Objective mạnh nhất</span>\n          <h3>O2 — AHV DTLX Build &amp; Evolve</h3>\n          <p>W4 Score: <strong>0.73</strong></p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"summary-card\">\n          <span>Tăng trưởng nhanh</span>\n          <h3>O3 — Multi AI Agent</h3>\n          <p>Start 0.10 → W4 <strong>0.74</strong></p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"summary-card\">\n          <span>Cần thêm evidence trực tiếp</span>\n          <h3>O1</h3>\n          <p>Chấm thận trọng, nên nối thêm repo chuyên biệt</p>\n        </article>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"evidence\">\n        <h2>Evidence Snapshot</h2>\n        <div class=\"evidence-grid\">\n          <div class=\"evidence-item\">\n            <strong>65</strong>\n            <span>agent/workspace trong hệ Multi Agent hiện tại</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"evidence-item\">\n            <strong>103 / 122</strong>\n            <span>commit FE trong giai đoạn W2 / W4</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"evidence-item\">\n            <strong>93 / 155</strong>\n            <span>commit BE trong giai đoạn W2 / W4</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"evidence-item\">\n            <strong>18+ modules</strong>\n            <span>Swagger / backend modules và flows đã triển khai</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section>\n        <h2>Objective Overview</h2>\n        <div class=\"objective-grid\">\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Objective 1</p>\n                <h3>AHV Landing Page V2</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status ontrack\">On Track</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>Đảm bảo Landing Page V2 vận hành ổn định trên production và được cập nhật theo yêu cầu nghiệp vụ.</p>\n            <div class=\"score-row\"><span>Start</span><strong>0.35</strong></div>\n            <div class=\"score-row\"><span>W2</span><strong>0.53</strong></div>\n            <div class=\"score-row\"><span>W4</span><strong>0.67</strong></div>\n            <p class=\"note\">Baseline tốt do đã production trước đó; cần repo riêng để chấm chắc hơn.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card featured\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Objective 2</p>\n                <h3>AHV DTLX — Build &amp; Evolve</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status strong\">Strong</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>Xây dựng mới hệ thống QLHV từ đầu (FE + BE) đồng thời refactor, tối ưu và nâng cấp CMS Trung tâm.</p>\n            <div class=\"score-row\"><span>Start</span><strong>0.17</strong></div>\n            <div class=\"score-row\"><span>W2</span><strong>0.53</strong></div>\n            <div class=\"score-row\"><span>W4</span><strong>0.73</strong></div>\n            <p class=\"note\">Evidence mạnh: 122 FE commits, 155 BE commits, RBAC, import, exam, finance, support request, CI/CD.</p>\n          </article>\n\n          <article class=\"objective-card\">\n            <div class=\"objective-head\">\n              <div>\n                <p class=\"tag\">Objective 3</p>\n                <h3>Multi AI Agent</h3>\n              </div>\n              <span class=\"status ontrack\">On Track</span>\n            </div>\n            <p>Nghiên cứu, triển khai và hình thành năng lực Multi Agent có thể tái sử dụng cho team.</p>\n            <div class=\"score-row\"><span>Start</span><strong>0.10</strong></div>\n            <div class=\"score-row\"><span>W2</span><strong>0.40</strong></div>\n            <div class=\"score-row\"><span>W4</span><strong>0.74</strong></div>\n            <p class=\"note\">Tăng trưởng nhanh, đã vượt mức nghiên cứu sang áp dụng thực tế.</p>\n          </article>\n\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section>\n        <h2>Detailed KR Scoring</h2>\n        <div class=\"table-wrap\">\n          <table>\n            <thead>\n              <tr>\n                <th>Objective</th>\n                <th>Key Result</th>\n                <th>Start</th>\n                <th>W2</th>\n                <th>W4</th>\n                <th>Status</th>\n                <th>Comment</th>\n              </tr>\n            </thead>\n            <tbody>\n              <tr><td>O1</td><td>KR1.1 Vận hành ổn định production</td><td>0.50</td><td>0.65</td><td>0.75</td><td>On Track</td><td>Đã có baseline production, tiến triển theo hướng ổn định vận hành.</td></tr>\n              <tr><td>O1</td><td>KR1.2 Xử lý change request</td><td>0.40</td><td>0.60</td><td>0.75</td><td>On Track</td><td>Tiến triển đều theo mô hình maintain + enhancement.</td></tr>\n              <tr><td>O1</td><td>KR1.3 Kiểm soát release quality</td><td>0.35</td><td>0.55</td><td>0.70</td><td>On Track</td><td>Có logic production discipline nhưng thiếu 