{"type":"message","id":"6ad24f38","parentId":"a14f3617","timestamp":"2026-04-23T07:56:25.713Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Let me give the user a summary of the changes.","thinkingSignature":"3fbc89ebbe0cf613d5c6b0bed5d17bfda44939bbf82ae077313d55d0d8b8dfcd"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Xong. Đã gộp O2 + O3 thành **1 objective ngắn gọn**.\n\n---\n\n### Cấu trúc OKR mới — 3 Objectives\n\n| | Objective | W4 Score |\n|---|---|---|\n| O1 | AHV Landing Page V2 | 0.67 |\n| **O2** | **AHV DTLX — Build & Evolve** | **0.73** |\n| O3 | Multi AI Agent | 0.74 |\n\n---\n\n### O2 gộp — AHV DTLX: Build & Evolve\n\n> **Xây dựng mới hệ thống QLHV từ đầu (FE + BE) đồng thời refactor, tối ưu và nâng cấp CMS Trung tâm.**\n\n| KR | Nội dung | W4 |\n|---|---|---|\n| KR2.1 | Nền tảng FE + BE mới (QLHV from scratch) | **0.83** |\n| KR2.2 | Integration FE-BE và end-to-end flows | **0.78** |\n| KR2.3 | Refactor & tối ưu CMS Trung tâm | 0.63 |\n| KR2.4 | Chuẩn hóa code, kiến trúc, docs | 0.70 |\n| KR2.5 | Review/demo readiness | 0.72 |\n\nEvidence: 122 FE commits, 155 BE commits, RBAC, import, exam, finance, support, CI/CD, swagger 18 modules.\n\nReport: <http://103.253.21.139:8790/reports/okr-review-w4-2026-04/>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":111,"output":401,"cacheRead":51192,"cacheWrite":564,"totalTokens":52268,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776930978390,"responseId":"063903a3d180d927b75e5a4b14ec1437"}}
