{"type":"message","id":"69a4bb00","parentId":"ecc2af7a","timestamp":"2026-04-23T08:47:43.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mình bắt đầu nâng toàn bộ portal thành docs site chính thức: chuẩn hóa homepage, regenerate tất cả trang theo cùng doc shell, rồi commit lại workspace.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_l8gSIiuq5pf7Ydr7kL5mTVoX","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/report-portal/index.html","offset":1,"limit":260}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_QSwtB6VWWPqNd7SDUlaeinrG","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/report-portal/reports/multi-agent-governance/index.html","offset":1,"limit":260}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_lYlfgoFpouboPL6l05EGGGwT","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/docs/convert.sh","offset":1,"limit":200}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-TroLy","usage":{"input":2680,"output":306,"cacheRead":73984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76970,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776934044915,"responseId":"1776934046766"}}
{"type":"message","id":"10818d3f","parentId":"69a4bb00","timestamp":"2026-04-23T08:47:43.154Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_l8gSIiuq5pf7Ydr7kL5mTVoX","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"vi\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"/>\n<title>Khương — Agent System Docs</title>\n<style>\n:root{--bg:#0b1020;--panel:#131a2e;--text:#eef3ff;--muted:#9fb0d0;--primary:#6ea8fe;--green:#3ddc97;--yellow:#f6c85f;--border:rgba(255,255,255,.08);--shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.25)}\n*{box-sizing:border-box}\nbody{margin:0;font-family:Inter,ui-sans-serif,system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;background:radial-gradient(circle at top,#17213d 0%,var(--bg) 55%);color:var(--text)}\n.page{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 24px 80px}\n.eyebrow{text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;font-size:12px;color:var(--primary);margin-bottom:8px;display:block}\nh1{margin:0 0 12px;font-size:42px;line-height:1.05}\n.subtitle{color:var(--muted);font-size:17px;line-height:1.65;max-width:760px;margin-bottom:0}\n.hero{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:24px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:36px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.meta-card{background:rgba(19,26,46,.86);border:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:var(--shadow);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-radius:20px;min-width:240px;padding:20px;display:grid;gap:12px}\n.meta-card span{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-bottom:4px}\n.meta-card strong{font-size:18px}\n.summary-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:36px}\n.summary-card{background:rgba(19,26,46,.86);border:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:var(--shadow);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-radius:20px;padding:16px 18px}\n.summary-card span{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:6px}\n.summary-card h3{margin:0;font-size:22px}\n.summary-card p{color:var(--muted);margin:4px 0 0;font-size:13px}\n.summary-card.strong{border-color:rgba(61,220,151,.3)}\nh2{margin:0 0 18px;font-size:22px}\n.section{margin-bottom:40px}\n.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px}\n.card{background:rgba(19,26,46,.86);border:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:var(--shadow);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-radius:20px;padding:22px;transition:transform .2s ease}\n.card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px)}\n.card-num{color:var(--primary);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;display:block}\n.card h3{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:19px;line-height:1.3}\n.card p{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 14px}\n.tag{display:inline-block;padding:2px 9px;border-radius:999px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em}\n.tag.foundation{background:rgba(110,168,254,.14);color:var(--primary)}\n.tag.operating{background:rgba(61,220,151,.14);color:var(--green)}\n.tag.maturity{background:rgba(246,200,95,.14);color:var(--yellow)}\n.tag.guide{background:rgba(61,220,151,.14);color:var(--green)}\n.tag.diagram{background:rgba(246,200,95,.14);color:var(--yellow)}\n.actions{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;min-height:36px;padding:0 14px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;transition:all .2s ease}\n.btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}\n.btn-primary{color:#07101f;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8ab9ff,#6ea8fe)}\n.btn-secondary{color:var(--text);background:rgba(255,255,255,.04)}\n.btn-sm{min-height:30px;padding:0 10px;font-size:12px;border-radius:8px}\n.footer{background:rgba(19,26,46,.86);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:24px}\n.footer h3{margin:0 0 12px;font-size:18px}\n.footer p{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin:0}\n@media(max-width:1024px){.summary-grid,.grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.hero{flex-direction:column}}\n@media(max-width:640px){.summary-grid,.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.page{padding:20px 16px 60px}h1{font-size:30px}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"page\">\n\n<header class=\"hero\">\n  <div>\n    <span class=\"eyebrow\">Agent System Documentation</span>\n    <h1>Multi-Agent Ecosystem</h1>\n    <p class=\"subtitle\">Bộ tài liệu đầy đủ về hệ Multi-Agent: tổng quan, taxonomy, orchestration, workflows, spec framework, governance, metrics, gap analysis, sơ đồ kiến trúc, và hướng dẫn sử dụng.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"meta-card\">\n    <div><span>Prepared by</span><strong>Khương Nịnh</strong></div>\n    <div><span>Total agents</span><strong>65 (38 + 27)</strong></div>\n    <div><span>Documents</span><strong>11 tài liệu</strong></div>\n    <div><span>System agents</span><strong>38 reusable</strong></div>\n    <div><span>DTLX agents</span><strong>27 project-specific</strong></div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n<div class=\"summary-grid\">\n  <div class=\"summary-card strong\">\n    <span>Maturity</span>\n    <h3>Level 2–3</h3>\n    <p>Repeatable → Defined</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"summary-card\">\n    <span>Canonical Workflows</span>\n    <h3>5 Workflows</h3>\n    <p>Docs, Code Review, Arch, Feature, QA</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"summary-card\">\n    <span>Authorization Levels</span>\n    <h3>4 Levels</h3>\n    <p>Read → Draft → Implement → Operational</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"summary-card\">\n    <span>Gaps Identified</span>\n    <h3>9 Gaps</h3>\n    <p>Priority matrix & 3-phase roadmap</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"section\">\n  <h2>🎯 Tài liệu dành cho mọi người</h2>\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Guide</span>\n      <span class=\"tag guide\">Non-Tech</span>\n      <h3>Hướng Dẫn Sử Dụng</h3>\n      <p>Hướng dẫn chi tiết cách đặt yêu cầu, quy trình làm việc, ví dụ thực tế, thuật ngữ — dành cho người dùng không chuyên kỹ thuật.</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/10-non-tech-guide.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/10-non-tech-guide.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Diagram</span>\n      <span class=\"tag diagram\">Visual</span>\n      <h3>Sơ Đồ Toàn Cảnh Hệ Thống</h3>\n      <p>Sơ đồ Mermaid luồng hoạt động, 5 workflow chính, escalation flow, bảng tổng hợp ai làm gì.</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/10b-system-architecture-diagram.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/10b-system-architecture-diagram.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"section\">\n  <h2>📚 Tài liệu kỹ thuật — Agent Governance</h2>\n  <div class=\"grid\">\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Doc 01</span>\n      <span class=\"tag foundation\">Foundation</span>\n      <h3>Multi-Agent Ecosystem Overview</h3>\n      <p>Tổng quan toàn cảnh: mục đích, cấu trúc, maturity assessment, strategic recommendations.</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/01-multi-agent-overview.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/01-multi-agent-overview.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Doc 02</span>\n      <span class=\"tag foundation\">Foundation</span>\n      <h3>Agent Taxonomy and Inventory</h3>\n      <p>Mô hình phân loại 4 lớp, inventory 65 agents (38 system + 27 DTLX), capability clusters.</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/02-agent-taxonomy-and-inventory.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/02-agent-taxonomy-and-inventory.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Doc 03</span>\n      <span class=\"tag operating\">Operating</span>\n      <h3>Orchestration Architecture</h3>\n      <p>Mô hình điều phối: intake, routing decision tree, handoff contracts, escalation model.</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/03-orchestration-architecture.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/03-orchestration-architecture.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Doc 04</span>\n      <span class=\"tag operating\">Operating</span>\n      <h3>Standard Workflows</h3>\n      <p>5 canonical workflows: Documentation, Code Review, Architecture, Feature Spec, QA — stage-by-stage.</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/04-standard-workflows.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/04-standard-workflows.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Doc 05</span>\n      <span class=\"tag operating\">Operating</span>\n      <h3>Agent Specification Framework</h3>\n      <p>Khuôn mẫu 11 sections bắt buộc cho AGENTS.md, ví dụ spec hoàn chỉnh, migration strategy.</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/05-agent-spec-framework.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/05-agent-spec-framework.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Doc 06</span>\n      <span class=\"tag operating\">Operating</span>\n      <h3>Governance and Operating Model</h3>\n      <p>4 authorization levels, file modification rules, external communication policy, lifecycle.</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/06-governance-and-operating-model.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/06-governance-and-operating-model.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Doc 07</span>\n      <span class=\"tag maturity\">Maturity</span>\n      <h3>Metrics, KPIs and Adoption</h3>\n      <p>13 metrics across 4 categories, dashboard structure, reporting cadence, maturity model (5 levels).</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/07-metrics-kpis-and-adoption.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/07-metrics-kpis-and-adoption.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Doc 08</span>\n      <span class=\"tag maturity\">Maturity</span>\n      <h3>Gap Analysis and Roadmap</h3>\n      <p>9 gaps phân tích theo severity/urgency/effort/impact. Priority matrix + 3-phase roadmap.</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/08-gap-analysis-and-roadmap.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/08-gap-analysis-and-roadmap.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"card\">\n      <span class=\"card-num\">Doc 09</span>\n      <span class=\"tag operating\">Operating</span>\n      <h3>Case Studies</h3>\n      <p>5 case studies thực chiến: Documentation, Code Review, Feature Spec, Performance, OKR Assessment.</p>\n      <div class=\"actions\">\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/09-case-studies.html\">📖 Đọc</a>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"./reports/multi-agent-governance/09-case-studies.md\" download>⬇️ .md</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer\">\n  <h3>Management Summary</h3>\n  <p>Hệ Multi-Agent hiện tại ở <strong>maturity Level 2–3</strong>: workflows có tồn tại nhưng chưa đồng đều và chưa được đo lường có hệ thống. 9 gaps đã được xác định và ưu tiên. Top 5 gaps cần giải quyết trước trong 1–3 tháng. Hệ thống đã chứng minh giá trị qua 5 case studies thực chiến.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776934063148}}
{"type":"message","id":"6313cc36","parentId":"10818d3f","timestamp":"2026-04-23T08:47:43.164Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_QSwtB6VWWPqNd7SDUlaeinrG","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"vi\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\"/>\n<title>Multi-Agent Ecosystem Documentation — Khương Reports</title>\n<style>\n:root{--bg:#0b1020;--panel:#131a2e;--panel2:#19233d;--text:#eef3ff;--muted:#9fb0d0;--primary:#6ea8fe;--green:#3ddc97;--yellow:#f6c85f;--border:rgba(255,255,255,.08);--shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.25)}\n*{box-sizing:border-box}\nbody{margin:0;font-family:Inter,ui-sans-serif,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\"Segoe UI\",sans-serif;background:radial-gradient(circle at top,#17213d 0%,var(--bg) 55%);color:var(--text)}\n.page{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 24px 80px}\n.eyebrow{text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;font-size:12px;color:var(--primary);margin-bottom:8px;display:block}\nh1{margin:0 0 12px;font-size:42px;line-height:1.05}\n.subtitle{color:var(--muted);font-size:17px;line-height:1.65;max-width:760px;margin-bottom:24px}\n.hero{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:24px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:32px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.meta-card,.doc-card,.summary-card{background:rgba(19,26,46,.86);border:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:var(--shadow);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-radius:20px}\n.meta-card{min-width:240px;padding:20px;display:grid;gap:12px}\n.meta-card span{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-bottom:4px}\n.meta-card strong{font-size:18px}\n.summary-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:32px}\n.summary-card{padding:16px 18px}\n.summary-card span{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:6px}\n.summary-card h3{margin:0;font-size:22px}\n.summary-card p{color:var(--muted);margin:4px 0 0;font-size:13px}\n.summary-card.strong{border-color:rgba(61,220,151,.3)}\n.summary-card.strong span{color:var(--green)}\nh2{margin:0 0 18px;font-size:24px}\n.doc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:32px}\n.doc-card{padding:20px;transition:transform .2s ease,box-shadow .2s ease}\n.doc-card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}\n.doc-num{color:var(--primary);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;display:block}\n.doc-card h3{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:18px;line-height:1.3}\n.doc-card p{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 14px}\n.tag{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:999px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em}\n.tag.foundation{background:rgba(110,168,254,.14);color:var(--primary)}\n.tag.operating{background:rgba(61,220,151,.14);color:var(--green)}\n.tag.foundation2{background:rgba(246,200,95,.14);color:var(--yellow)}\n.actions{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-top:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}\n.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;min-height:36px;padding:0 14px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;transition:all .2s ease}\n.btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.2)}\n.btn-primary{color:#07101f;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8ab9ff,#6ea8fe)}\n.btn-secondary{color:var(--text);background:rgba(255,255,255,.04)}\n.btn-sm{min-height:30px;padding:0 10px;font-size:12px;border-radius:8px}\n.footer-note{background:rgba(19,26,46,.86);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:24px}\n.footer-note h2{margin:0 0 14px;font-size:20px}\n.footer-note ul{margin:0;padding-left:20px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8}\n.footer-note li{margin-bottom:6px}\n@media(max-width:1024px){.summary-grid,.doc-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.hero{flex-direction:column}}\n@media(max-width:640px){.summary-grid,.doc-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.page{padding:20px 16px 60px}h1{font-size:30px}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"page\">\n\n<header class=\"hero\">\n  <div>\n    <span class=\"eyebrow\">Agent Governance Suite</span>\n    <h1>Multi-Agent Ecosystem Documentation</h1>\n    <p class=\"subtitle\">Bộ tài liệu đầy đủ về hệ Multi-Agent: tổng quan, taxonomy, orchestration, workflows, spec framework, governance, metrics, gap analysis, và case studies thực chiến.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"meta-card\">\n    <div><span>Prepared by</span><strong>Khương Nịnh</strong></div>\n    <div><span>Documents</span><strong>10 tài liệu</strong></div>\n    <div><span>Total agents</span><strong>65 (38 + 27)</strong></div>\n    <div><span>Total content</span><strong>2,072 dòng</strong></div>\n    <div><span>Status</span><strong>Ready for Confluence</strong></div>\n  </div>\n</header>\n\n<div class=\"summary-grid\">\n  <div class=\"summary-card strong\">\n    <span>Maturity Stage</span>\n    <h3>Level 2–3</h3>\n    <p>Repeatable → Defined</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"summary-card\">\n    <span>System Agents</span>\n    <h3>38</h3>\n    <p>Generic, reusable across projects</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"summary-card\">\n    <span>DTLX Project Agents</span>\n    <h3>27</h3>\n    <p>Project-specific sessions</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"summary-card\">\n    <span>Gaps Identified</span>\n    <h3>9 Gaps</h3>\n    <p>Prioritized by severity</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>📚 Tài liệu kỹ thuật — Đọc trên web + Tải về</h2>\n\n<div class=\"doc-grid\" style=\"margin-bottom:32px\">\n  <article class=\"doc-card\" style=\"background:rgba(61,220,151,.06);border-color:rgba(61,220,151,.25)\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Guide</span>\n    <span class=\"tag\" style=\"background:rgba(61,220,151,.14);color:var(--green)\">For Everyone</span>\n    <h3>Hướng Dẫn Sử Dụng Cho Người Dùng</h3>\n    <p>Tài liệu hướng dẫn chi tiết dành cho người dùng không chuyên kỹ thuật. Bao gồm: cách đặt yêu cầu, quy trình làm việc, ví dụ thực tế, và các thuật ngữ thường gặp.</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./10-non-tech-guide.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/10-non-tech-guide.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n  <article class=\"doc-card\" style=\"background:rgba(246,200,95,.06);border-color:rgba(246,200,95,.3)\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Diagram</span>\n    <span class=\"tag\" style=\"background:rgba(246,200,95,.14);color:var(--yellow)\">Visual</span>\n    <h3>Sơ Đồ Toàn Cảnh Hệ Thống Agent</h3>\n    <p>Sơ đồ luồng hoạt động từ lúc người dùng đưa yêu cầu → điều phối → chuyên gia → tổng hợp → kết quả. Bao gồm: 5 workflow chính, escalation flow, và bảng tổng hợp.</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./10b-system-architecture-diagram.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/10b-system-architecture-diagram.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n</div>\n\n<h2>📚 Tài liệu kỹ thuật — Đọc trên web + Tải về</h2>\n<div class=\"doc-grid\">\n\n  <article class=\"doc-card\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Doc 01</span>\n    <span class=\"tag foundation\">Foundation</span>\n    <h3>Multi-Agent Ecosystem Overview</h3>\n    <p>Tổng quan toàn cảnh hệ Multi-Agent: mục đích, cấu trúc, maturity assessment, và strategic recommendations.</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./01-multi-agent-overview.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/01-multi-agent-overview.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n  <article class=\"doc-card\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Doc 02</span>\n    <span class=\"tag foundation\">Foundation</span>\n    <h3>Agent Taxonomy and Inventory</h3>\n    <p>Mô hình phân loại 4 lớp agent và inventory đầy đủ. 65+ agents được phân loại theo layer và capability.</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./02-agent-taxonomy-and-inventory.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/02-agent-taxonomy-and-inventory.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n  <article class=\"doc-card\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Doc 03</span>\n    <span class=\"tag operating\">Operating</span>\n    <h3>Orchestration Architecture</h3>\n    <p>Mô hình kiến trúc điều phối: intake, routing, specialist execution, consolidation. Routing decision tree + escalation model.</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./03-orchestration-architecture.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/03-orchestration-architecture.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n  <article class=\"doc-card\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Doc 04</span>\n    <span class=\"tag operating\">Operating</span>\n    <h3>Standard Workflows</h3>\n    <p>5 canonical workflows chuẩn: Documentation, Code Review, Architecture, Feature Spec, QA and Test Planning. Mỗi workflow có stage-by-stage breakdown.</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./04-standard-workflows.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/04-standard-workflows.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n  <article class=\"doc-card\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Doc 05</span>\n    <span class=\"tag operating\">Operating</span>\n    <h3>Agent Specification Framework</h3>\n    <p>Khuôn mẫu chuẩn cho mọi agent: 11 sections bắt buộc, ví dụ spec hoàn chỉnh, migration strategy.</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./05-agent-spec-framework.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/05-agent-spec-framework.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n  <article class=\"doc-card\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Doc 06</span>\n    <span class=\"tag operating\">Operating</span>\n    <h3>Governance and Operating Model</h3>\n    <p>Chính sách vận hành: 4 authorization levels, file modification rules, external communication policy, escalation, lifecycle, safety.</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./06-governance-and-operating-model.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/06-governance-and-operating-model.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n  <article class=\"doc-card\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Doc 07</span>\n    <span class=\"tag foundation2\">Maturity</span>\n    <h3>Metrics, KPIs and Adoption</h3>\n    <p>13 specific metrics across 4 categories. Dashboard structure, reporting cadence, adoption maturity model (5 levels).</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./07-metrics-kpis-and-adoption.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/07-metrics-kpis-and-adoption.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n  <article class=\"doc-card\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Doc 08</span>\n    <span class=\"tag foundation2\">Maturity</span>\n    <h3>Gap Analysis and Roadmap</h3>\n    <p>9 gaps được phân tích: severity, urgency, effort, impact. Priority matrix + 3-phase roadmap.</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./08-gap-analysis-and-roadmap.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/08-gap-analysis-and-roadmap.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n  <article class=\"doc-card\">\n    <span class=\"doc-num\">Doc 09</span>\n    <span class=\"tag operating\">Operating</span>\n    <h3>Case Studies</h3>\n    <p>5 case studies thực chiến: Documentation, Code Review, Feature Spec, Performance, OKR Assessment. Template cho future use.</p>\n    <div class=\"actions\">\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"./09-case-studies.html\">📖 Đọc trên web</a>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-sm\" href=\"../../../../docs/09-case-studies.md\" download>⬇️ Tải .md</a>\n    </div>\n  </article>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer-note\">\n  <h2>Management Conclusion</h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li>Hệ Multi-Agent hiện tại ở <strong>maturity Level 2–3</strong>: workflows có tồn tại nhưng chưa đồng đều và chưa được đo lường có hệ thống.</li>\n    <li>9 gaps đã được xác định và ưu tiên theo severity và impact. <strong>Top 5 gaps</strong> cần giải quyết trước trong 1–3 tháng.</li>\n    <li>Hệ thống đã chứng minh giá trị qua <strong>5 case studies</strong> thực chiến. Bước tiếp theo là chuẩn hóa, đo lường, và mở rộng.</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776934063156}}
